withdraw.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller has the DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the receiver is the zero address
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the receiver is not the zero address
      └─ it should withdraw the correct asset and amount to the correct address
